      <a name="maincontent" id="maincontent"></a>
      <h2><a name="ua" id="ua"></a>Undergraduate admissions</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="http://admissions.berkeley.edu">Admissions &mdash; Undergraduate</a>:
          Requirements, deadlines, answers to frequently asked questions,
          and more. </li>
        <li><a href="https://students.berkeley.edu/myberkeley/myberkeleyapp.asp">MyBerkeleyApplication</a>:
          Online site for navigating the admissions process, designed for
          applicants, new students, and their parents.</li>
        <li><a href="http://www.universityofcalifornia.edu/admissions/undergrad_adm/apply/apply_online.html">Undergraduate
          applications online</a>: Submit applications to the UC system
          online.</li>
        <li><a href="http://statfinder.ucop.edu/">UC undergraduate admissions
          and enrollment data</a>:  Detailed data on undergraduate admissions
          and enrollment at the University of California.</li>
        <li><a href="/catalog/curricula.html">UC Berkeley
          courses and curricula by department</a></li>
        </ul>
      <hr />
      <h2><a name="ga" id="ga"></a>Graduate admissions</h2>
      <ul>
        
        <li><a href="http://www.grad.berkeley.edu/admissions/">Admissions
          &mdash; Graduate</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://www.grad.berkeley.edu/programs/">Graduate programs
          and application deadlines</a>: Complete list.</li>
        <li><a href="/about/rank.shtml">National rankings of graduate programs</a></li>
        <li><a href="/catalog/curricula.html">Courses
          and curricula by department</a></li>
        </ul>
      
      <hr />
      <h2><a name="oa" id="oa"></a>Transfer, re-entry, and student parents </h2>
      <ul>
        
        <li><a href="http://trsp.berkeley.edu/">Transfer,
          Re-Entry &amp; Student
          Parent Center</a>: For students transferring  from other colleges
          and other universities, older students returning to school, and
          students with families. </li>
        <li><a href="http://students.berkeley.edu/admissions/transfer.asp">Transfer-student
          admission statistics and guidelines</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://www.ocf.berkeley.edu/~spa/">Student Parent Association</a></li>
        </ul>
      <hr />
      <h2><a name="ia" id="ia"></a>International student admissions </h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="http://students.berkeley.edu/admissions/freshmen.asp?id=55&amp;navid=N">Freshmen
          international applicants</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://students.berkeley.edu/admissions/transfer.asp?id=62&amp;navid=N">Transfer
          international applicants</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://www.grad.berkeley.edu/admissions/admis_require.shtml#4_2">Graduate
          international applicant admission criteria </a></li>
        </ul>
      <hr />
      <h2><a name="dsp" id="dsp"></a>Disabled Students' Program</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="http://dsp.berkeley.edu/">Disabled Students' Program</a></li>
        </ul>    
      <hr />
      <h2><a name="fees" id="fees"></a>Fees, finances &amp; aid</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="http://registrar.berkeley.edu/Registration/feesched.html">Fees</a>:
          Undergraduate, graduate, and professional schools. </li>
        <li><a href="/about/fact.shtml#fees">Student
          budgets</a>: Annual
          estimates of the total cost of attending Berkeley.</li>
        <li><a href="/apply/aid.shtml">Financial aid, scholarships, &amp; fellowships</a></li>
        </ul>
      <hr />
      <h2><a name="summer" id="summer"></a>Summer Sessions &amp; Lifelong Learning</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="http://summer.berkeley.edu/">Summer sessions</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://www.unex.berkeley.edu">UC Berkeley Extension</a>:
          Accredited continuing-education courses.</li>
        <li><a href="http://extension.berkeley.edu/online/">UC Berkeley Extension
          online</a>: Accredited online courses.</li>
        <li><a href="http://executive.berkeley.edu/">Executive Development
          Program</a>: Haas School of Business program for business executives.</li>
        </ul>
